[26/09/2017 03:01:41] <font color="#ffff00">Vale.</font>
[26/09/2017 03:01:42] <font color="#ffff00">"France me pide</font>
[26/09/2017 03:01:42] <font color="#ffff00">que pique las cebollas</font>
