[26/09/2017 19:40:07] <font color="#0000ff">Yo te siento.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:40:14] <font color="#0000ff">(Timbre)</font>
[26/09/2017 19:40:19] <font color="#ffff00">Hola, Nathalie.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:40:19] <font color="#ffffff">Hola.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:40:20] <font color="#ffff00">Un beso.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:40:24] <font color="#ffff00">Traigo harina porque he visitado</font>
