[26/09/2017 19:44:43] <font color="#ffffff">Solo lo justo.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:44:43] <font color="#ffff00">De Alsacia.</font>
[26/09/2017 19:44:46] <font color="#ffffff">Es igual.</font>
